transArray.content:
Very satisfied

Hygiene: Very clean and tidy
Environment: very good
Service: Very enthusiastic. Will come again next time
There are also small robots delivering food

Dear, thank you for your praise. Your satisfaction is the driving force for us to move forward. Your recognition has brought us a little bit of coolness in the hot summer. We will continue to work hard to welcome you with warm service and a clean and comfortable sanitary environment. Come and wish you and your family all the best.
